FBIS4-28655 "dreas113_a_94012" FBIS-EAS-94-113 Daily Report 13 Jun 1994 NORTHEAST ASIA Japan Reports on Issues Related to DPRK Continue Reports on Issues Related to DPRK Continue KCNA on DPRK Withdrawal From IAEA OW1306144294 Tokyo KYODO in English 1432 GMT 13 Jun 94 OW1306144294 Tokyo KYODO English BFN [Text] Tokyo, June 13 KYODO -- North Korea said Monday it will immediately withdraw from the International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA), the official (North) KOREAN CENTRAL NEWS AGENCY (KCNA) reported. The KCNA report, monitored by the Tokyo-based KOREA NEWS SERVICE, quoted a North Korean Foreign Ministry spokesman as saying. [sentence as received]
